{"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Custom application language for push notifications."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"language"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"set","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Override the device language for notification content localization. This affects which language version of your push notifications is delivered from Pushwoosh servers.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Format","anchor":"Format","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Use lowercase two-letter ISO-639-1 language codes:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"\"en\"","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" - English","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"de\""},{"type":"text","text":" - German"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"\"fr\"","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" - French","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"es\""},{"type":"text","text":" - Spanish"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"ru\""},{"text":" - Russian","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"\"ja\"","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" - Japanese","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Default-Behavior","level":2,"text":"Default Behavior"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, Pushwoosh uses